PROBLEM STATEMENT 1

As Colaberry continues to gain popularity in the Data Analytics field, enrollments are skyrocketing. In 2017 enrollment went up by 50%, in 2018 it was up by 18.18%, in 2019 it went up 25.64%, and 51% in 2020.

With the increase in class size, it is important for Colaberry to ensure that Instructor quality remains consistent.
